{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I recognized the roles\nthat were placed on me very early."},{"time":5932,"text":"One persistent concept that I observed --"},{"time":9006,"text":"existing in our language, in our media --"},{"time":11387,"text":"was that women are not only\nsupposed to have children,"},{"time":17340,"text":"they are supposed to want to."},{"time":20558,"text":"This existed everywhere."},{"time":22527,"text":"It existed in the ways\nthat adults spoke to me"},{"time":26576,"text":"when they posed questions\nin the context of \"when.\""},{"time":31577,"text":"\"When you get married ...\""},{"time":33482,"text":"\"When you have kids ...\""},{"time":36806,"text":"And these future musings\nwere always presented to me"},{"time":39830,"text":"like part of this American dream,"},{"time":42655,"text":"but it always felt to me\nlike someone else's dream."},{"time":45368,"text":"You see, a value that I have\nalways understood about myself"},{"time":49623,"text":"was that I never wanted children."},{"time":52996,"text":"And as a kid, when I would try\nto explain this,"},{"time":56861,"text":"this disconnect between\ntheir roles and my values,"},{"time":60694,"text":"they often laughed"},{"time":62334,"text":"in the way that adults do\nat the absurdities of children."},{"time":66770,"text":"And they would tell me knowingly,"},{"time":68572,"text":"\"You'll change your mind.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":71782,"text":"And people have been saying\nthings like that to me my whole life."},{"time":75406,"text":"Otherwise polite conversation\ncan turn intrusive fast."},{"time":81366,"text":"\"Does your husband know?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":83112,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":85943,"text":"\"Do your parents know?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":87316,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":89132,"text":"\"Don't you want a family?\""},{"time":92463,"text":"\"Don't you want to leave anything behind?\""},{"time":96106,"text":"And the primary buzzword\nwhen discussing childlessness,"},{"time":102001,"text":"\"That's selfish.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":107252,"text":"There are countless reasons\na woman may have"},{"time":110609,"text":"for choosing to abstain from motherhood,"},{"time":113729,"text":"the majority of them\nnot self-prioritizing."},{"time":118094,"text":"But it is still socially acceptable\nto publicly vilify women as such,"},{"time":122420,"text":"because none of these reasons\nhave made it into the social narrative."},{"time":126482,"text":"When I was little and learning\nabout the inevitability of maternity,"},{"time":132189,"text":"it was never explained to me"},{"time":133956,"text":"the commonness of these factors\nthat women consider,"},{"time":139718,"text":"like the risk of passing on\nhereditary illness,"},{"time":142155,"text":"the danger of having to stop\nlife-saving medication"},{"time":145337,"text":"for the duration of your pregnancy,"},{"time":147300,"text":"concern about overpopulation,"},{"time":149452,"text":"your access to resources,"},{"time":152269,"text":"and the fact that there are\n415,000 children"},{"time":157942,"text":"in the foster-care system\nin the United States at any given time."},{"time":162842,"text":"Reasons like these, many more,"},{"time":166772,"text":"and the fact that I don't like to leave\nthings of this magnitude to chance,"},{"time":171748,"text":"all informed my decision"},{"time":174130,"text":"to become surgically sterilized."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177023,"text":"I began my research eagerly."},{"time":180433,"text":"I wanted to fully understand"},{"time":182048,"text":"all that was going to come\nwith undergoing a tubal ligation,"},{"time":187477,"text":"which is just another word\nfor getting your tubes tied."},{"time":190809,"text":"I wanted to know approval to aftermath,"},{"time":194163,"text":"satisfaction rates, risks, statistics."},{"time":198171,"text":"And at first, I was empowered."},{"time":200529,"text":"You see, the way the narrative\nhas always been taught to me,"},{"time":204275,"text":"I would have thought that women\nwho didn't want children were so rare,"},{"time":208567,"text":"and then I learned\none in five American women"},{"time":212370,"text":"won't be having a biological child --"},{"time":214711,"text":"some by choice, some by chance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217568,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":218781,"text":"But I was not alone."},{"time":223192,"text":"But the more I read,\nthe more disheartened I became."},{"time":225931,"text":"I read women's stories,"},{"time":228762,"text":"trying desperately to get this procedure."},{"time":232534,"text":"I learned how common it was\nfor women to exhaust their finances"},{"time":238953,"text":"appealing to dozens of ob-gyns\nover many years,"},{"time":245921,"text":"only to be turned down so many times,"},{"time":247807,"text":"often with such blatant disrespect\nthat they just gave up."},{"time":251529,"text":"Women reported that medical practitioners\nwere often condescending"},{"time":258189,"text":"and dismissive of their motivations,"},{"time":262236,"text":"being told things like,"},{"time":264213,"text":"\"Come back when you're married\nwith a child.\""},{"time":268865,"text":"But women who did have children,\nwho went to go get this procedure,"},{"time":272877,"text":"were told they were too young,"},{"time":275707,"text":"or they didn't have enough children,"},{"time":279072,"text":"which is very interesting,"},{"time":281049,"text":"because the legal requirements in my state\nfor getting this kind of surgery were,"},{"time":288160,"text":"\"Be at least 21 years old,\""},{"time":291287,"text":"\"appear of sound mind,\nacting of your own accord,\""},{"time":294249,"text":"and \"have a 30-day waiting period.\""},{"time":298345,"text":"And I was perplexed that I could meet\nall of these legal requirements"},{"time":304067,"text":"and still have to face a battle\nin the exam room"},{"time":307202,"text":"for my bodily autonomy."},{"time":309957,"text":"And it was daunting,"},{"time":312468,"text":"but I was determined."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314664,"text":"I remember I dressed so professionally\nto that first appointment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319988,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":321189,"text":"I sat up straight."},{"time":322880,"text":"I spoke clearly."},{"time":325292,"text":"I wanted to give that doctor\nevery piece of evidence"},{"time":330189,"text":"that I was not the date\nof birth in that file."},{"time":334643,"text":"And I made sure to mention things like,"},{"time":337148,"text":"\"I just got my bachelor's degree"},{"time":338863,"text":"and I'm applying\nto these doctoral programs,"},{"time":341450,"text":"I'm going to study these things.\""},{"time":343405,"text":"And \"my long-term partner\nhas this kind of business,\""},{"time":347567,"text":"and \"I've done research\non this for months."},{"time":351017,"text":"I understand everything\nabout it, all the risks.\""},{"time":354615,"text":"Because I needed the doctor to know\nthat this was not a whim,"},{"time":358347,"text":"not reactionary,"},{"time":360332,"text":"not your 20-something\nlooking to go out and party"},{"time":363808,"text":"without fear of getting knocked up ..."},{"time":365952,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":367944,"text":"that this supported something\nintegral to who I was."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373237,"text":"And I understand informed consent,"},{"time":374901,"text":"so I fully expected to be reeducated\non how it all worked, but ..."},{"time":382909,"text":"At one point, the information being\ngiven to me started to feel agenda'd,"},{"time":387814,"text":"interlaced with bias\nand inflated statistics."},{"time":393603,"text":"The questions began to feel interrogative."},{"time":397885,"text":"At first they were asking me questions"},{"time":400371,"text":"that seemed to understand\nmy situation better,"},{"time":403854,"text":"and then it seemed like they were\nasking questions to try to trip me up."},{"time":407291,"text":"I felt like I was on the witness stand,\nbeing cross-examined."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412651,"text":"The doctor asked me about my partner."},{"time":415029,"text":"\"How does he or she\nfeel about all of this?\""},{"time":418460,"text":"\"Well, I've been with\nthe same man for five years,"},{"time":421961,"text":"and he fully supports any decision\nI make for my body.\""},{"time":425139,"text":"And he said, \"Well,\nwhat happens in the future,"},{"time":427744,"text":"if you change partners?"},{"time":428919,"text":"What happens when that person\nwants children?\""},{"time":432767,"text":"And I didn't quite know\nhow to react to that,"},{"time":436943,"text":"because what I was hearing"},{"time":438983,"text":"was this doctor tell me that I'm supposed\nto disregard everything I believe"},{"time":445980,"text":"if a partner demands children."},{"time":448804,"text":"So I told him not to worry about that."},{"time":451988,"text":"My stance on childbearing\nhas always been first date conversation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":455597,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":461708,"text":"(Cheering)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":462882,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":467253,"text":"He then asks me to consider"},{"time":471531,"text":"how \"in 20 years, you could really\ncome to regret this\" ..."},{"time":476848,"text":"as though I hadn't."},{"time":479654,"text":"I told him,"},{"time":484156,"text":"\"OK, if I wake up one day"},{"time":488555,"text":"and realize, you know,"},{"time":491627,"text":"I wish I'd made a different\ndecision back then,"},{"time":496856,"text":"the truth is, I'd only removed\na single path to parenthood."},{"time":500973,"text":"I never needed biology\nto form family anyway.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":504356,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":512892,"text":"And I would much rather\ndeal with that any day"},{"time":516701,"text":"than deal with one day waking up,"},{"time":519694,"text":"realize I'd had a child"},{"time":523688,"text":"that I didn't really want\nor was prepared to care for."},{"time":529633,"text":"Because one of these affects only me."},{"time":532873,"text":"The other affects a child,"},{"time":535364,"text":"their development, their well-being --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":537674,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":541357,"text":"and human beings\nare not to be gambled with."},{"time":546058,"text":"He then tells me why no one\nwas going to approve this procedure,"},{"time":552109,"text":"certainly not he,"},{"time":553648,"text":"because of a concept\ncalled medical paternalism,"},{"time":556911,"text":"which allows him,\nas my well-informed provider,"},{"time":562000,"text":"to make decisions for me ..."},{"time":565481,"text":"based on his perception\nof my best interest,"},{"time":568318,"text":"regardless of what I,\nas the patient, want or believe."},{"time":572800,"text":"He takes this opportunity to step out"},{"time":575809,"text":"and discuss my case\nwith my potential surgeon,"},{"time":579729,"text":"and through the door, I hear him\ndescribe me as a little girl."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589137,"text":"I was so offended."},{"time":591434,"text":"I wanted to defend myself."},{"time":593412,"text":"I wanted to explicitly explain\nto each one of these providers"},{"time":597857,"text":"how they were treating me,"},{"time":599201,"text":"that it was belittling and sexist,"},{"time":601650,"text":"and I didn't have to take it."},{"time":607082,"text":"But I did take it."},{"time":610211,"text":"I swallowed every sharp word in my throat,"},{"time":614501,"text":"clenched my jaw, and instead"},{"time":617562,"text":"answered each one of their condescending\nquestions and statements."},{"time":624595,"text":"I had come here looking\nfor objectivity and support"},{"time":628601,"text":"and instead I felt dismissed and silenced,"},{"time":632692,"text":"and I hated myself for it."},{"time":634085,"text":"I hated that I was letting people\ndisrespect me repeatedly."},{"time":639918,"text":"But this was my one shot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":645424,"text":"That was one of multiple consultations\nthat I had to go to."},{"time":650967,"text":"At one point, I had seen five or six\nmedical professionals in the same hour."},{"time":655891,"text":"The door to the exam room\nfelt more like the door to a clown car."},{"time":659439,"text":"There's my primary,"},{"time":660829,"text":"there's his colleague,"},{"time":662661,"text":"the director, OK."},{"time":665178,"text":"It felt like I was asking them\nto infect me with smallpox"},{"time":670598,"text":"instead of, I don't know,\nobtain birth control."},{"time":676787,"text":"But I didn't waver,"},{"time":681153,"text":"and I was persistent,"},{"time":683424,"text":"and I eventually convinced one of them\nto allow the procedure."},{"time":690790,"text":"And even as I am in the room,\nsigning the consent forms"},{"time":696084,"text":"and getting the hormone shots\nand tying up loose ends ..."},{"time":701556,"text":"my doctor is shaking\nhis head in disapproval."},{"time":707335,"text":"\"You'll change your mind.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":711542,"text":"I never really understood"},{"time":714805,"text":"how strongly this society\nclings to this role"},{"time":719185,"text":"until I went through this."},{"time":721556,"text":"I experienced firsthand, repeatedly,"},{"time":728908,"text":"how people, be it medical providers,"},{"time":734175,"text":"colleagues, strangers,"},{"time":738554,"text":"were literally unable\nto separate me being a woman"},{"time":745261,"text":"from me being a mother."},{"time":748191,"text":"And I've always believed\nthat having children"},{"time":752804,"text":"was an extension of womanhood,\nnot the definition."},{"time":756728,"text":"I believe that a woman's value"},{"time":759428,"text":"should never be determined\nby whether or not she has a child,"},{"time":763934,"text":"because that strips her\nof her entire identity"},{"time":768102,"text":"as an adult unto herself."},{"time":770492,"text":"Women have this amazing ability\nto create life,"},{"time":775185,"text":"but when we say that that is her purpose,"},{"time":779414,"text":"that says that her entire existence\nis a means to an end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":788995,"text":"It's so easy to forget the roles\nthat society places on us"},{"time":793175,"text":"are so much more than mere titles."},{"time":795432,"text":"What about the weight\nthat comes with them,"},{"time":798020,"text":"the pressure to conform\nto these standards ..."},{"time":801169,"text":"the fear associated with questioning them,"},{"time":804375,"text":"and the desires that we\ncast aside to accept them?"},{"time":808841,"text":"There are many paths\nto happiness and fulfillment."},{"time":812222,"text":"They all look very different,"},{"time":814217,"text":"but I believe that every one"},{"time":818964,"text":"is paved with the right\nto self-determination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825951,"text":"I want women to know that your choice\nto embrace or forego motherhood"},{"time":834546,"text":"is not in any way tied\nto your worthiness or identity"},{"time":838341,"text":"as spouses, as adults, or as women ..."},{"time":843820,"text":"and there absolutely is\na choice behind maternity,"},{"time":848182,"text":"and it is yours"},{"time":850008,"text":"and yours alone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":851645,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":852820,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}